- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper discusses the optimization aspect of the general-valued CSP, which is a common problem in artificial intelligence. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science): The paper uses algebraic conditions to determine the tractability of the general-valued CSP, which is related to logic in computer science.
